items.title: Awesome Incident Response
items.content_text:
### IR Tools Collection / Memory Analysis Tools

*   [MalConfScan (⭐489)](https://github.com/JPCERTCC/MalConfScan) - MalConfScan is a Volatility plugin extracts configuration data of known malware. Volatility is an open-source memory forensics framework for incident response and malware analysis. This tool searches for malware in memory images and dumps configuration data. In addition, this tool has a function to list strings to which malicious code refers.
items.content_html:
